data.message: QA review of Duro Dashboard implementation: Identified 7 issues: (1) Stats grid missing logs (55% of data), (2) Memory browser dropdown missing 6 artifact types, (3) Titles truncated aggressively, (4) Load More button not functional, (5) No click-to-view detail, (6) Activity feed empty on load, (7) Sidebar nav decorative only. Recommended 6 improvements prioritized by impact.
